Detailed Description

Representation of one grid cell.

This structure represents a map cell for those occasions where individual grid cells are passed between function and classes. It is primarily used with the MapStore::trace() function and the MapStoreTrace class returned by that function.

The MapStore class itself uses another, more memory-efficient internal representation.
